\pc \bd 181\bd*

\s Uchunge wakati kusema na Bwana
\zon1 1
\zoli1 \bd Uchunge wakati kusema na Bwana\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Na vile kusoma Neno takatifu\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Fanya urafiki na wenye imani\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Na omba baraka kwa neno lo lote.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Uchunge wakati, saa inakimbia\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Ushinde saa zote pamoja na Bwana\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Ukimutazama, utabadilishwa Kupata mufano wa Yesu hakika.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Uchunge wakati, atakuongoza\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Umutegemee kwa mambo yo yote\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Katika furaha, katika huzuni, Umutumaini, atakushindisha.\bd*
\b 
\zoli1 \bd Uchunge wakati, salama moyoni\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Yesu atawale hata mafikili\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Atakufundisha na Roho ya kweli\bd*\bd ;\bd*\bd  Utatayarishwa kufika\bd*\bd  Mbingu\bd*\bd ni.\bd*
